New York Jets Linebacker Bryan Thomas Is Out for Year With Achilles Injury

-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 
2011-10-04T12:40:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/new-york-jets-linebacker-bryan-thomas-is-out-for-year-with-achilles-injury.html
New York Jets linebacker Bryan Thomas
will miss the remainder of the season after tearing his left
Achilles tendon two days ago in a loss to the  Baltimore Ravens .  “That’s going to be a huge loss for us,” coach  Rex Ryan 
said during a televised news conference.  Thomas, 32, was selected in the first round of the 2002
National Football League draft. He had 14 tackles this season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  